	INSTALL

	1. Preparation
	2. Compile
	3. Install

----------

1. Preparation

- Copy the file config/config.conf (for example) to /etc/vnstat-cgi/
- Copy the directory lang/ (for example) to /usr/share/vnstat-cgi/
- Open the file src/defines.h and modify the macros CONFIG_PATH and LANG_PATH to suit your needs

2. Compile

$ make

3. Install

- Copy the file vnstat-cgi to the cgi-bin of your webserver
